st-ps5-ssd-expansion-upgrade-150052315.html">the best SSDs for the console</a> . If you aren&#39;t buying for a PS5 specifically, the <a data-i13n="cpos:48;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAQziYbw7u44Ajjxsgxqyqc16DFVnN9LqnmU7ZG0g0QV7&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB08GLX7TNT%2F%3Fth%3D1">non-heatsink model</a> is available for a few dollars less, though a speedy PCIe 4.0 drive like this may be overkill for some.</p><h2> Apple iPad (9th gen) </h2><p><core-commerce id="ce8f33951a97436a9b137278dc8e9a81" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> The 64GB model of <a data-i13n="cpos:49;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS8yMDIxLUFwcGxlLTEwLTItaW5jaC1pUGFkLVdpLUZpL2RwL0IwOUc5Q0pNMVo_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tMTRhLTIwIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiI3OTE3YzIyYS03ODg5LTRjMzItYTJkOS05NWFhY2RhMWQyMTEifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAaQy6KVh84S90Pb4sYdIUB-5aX2LJh6m4aCLC9TaI-lM&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2F2021-Apple-10-2-inch-iPad-Wi-Fi%2Fdp%2FB09G9CJM1Z">Apple&#39;s 9th-gen iPad</a> is down to $250 at Amazon, matching the lowest price we&#39;ve tracked. You should see the full discount at checkout. Apple normally sells the device for $329, though we&#39;ve seen it retail closer to $275 in recent months. This is the budget pick in <a data-i13n="cpos:50;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/best-ipads-how-to-pick-the-best-apple-tablet-for-you-150054066.html">our iPad buying guide</a> : I